OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy tonight with occasional
OL,7,Foutbreaks of light and patchy rain,
OL,8,Fespecially across the high ground of
OL,9,FCumbria and Lancashire. A mild night
OL,10,Facross the region under the blanket of
OL,11,Fcloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAnother rather cloudy day with
OL,14,Ffurther outbreaks of rain. Rain will
OL,15,Fbe light at first, but may turn
OL,16,Fheavier across the north in the
OL,17,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
